JackNullOption

public static final JackOptions JackNullOption
Null value to use when no option bits are needed. Not strictly needed but here for completeness.

JackNoStartServer

public static final JackOptions JackNoStartServer
Do not automatically start the JACK server when it is not already running. This option is always selected if \$JACK_NO_START_SERVER is defined in the calling process environment.

JackUseExactName

public static final JackOptions JackUseExactName
Use the exact client name requested. Otherwise, JACK automatically generates a unique one, if needed.

JackLoadName

public static final JackOptions JackLoadName
Load internal client from optional (char *) load_name. Otherwise use the @a client_name. Not currently supported by JNAJack

JackLoadInit

public static final JackOptions JackLoadInit
Pass optional (char *) load_init string to the jack_initialize() entry point of an internal client. Not currently supported by JNAJack
